definitions.definition: A village and civil parish in North Kesteven district, Lincolnshire , England ( OS grid ref TF0043 ) .
A village and civil parish in the Vale of Pewsey , Wiltshire , England ( OS grid ref SU1057 ) . The parish council is joint with Charlton St Peter parish.
A settlement in Wilsford cum Lake parish, Wiltshire ( OS grid ref SU1339 ) .
